'''通用第二因素'''（{{lang-en|Universal 2nd Factor}}，縮寫'''U2F'''）是一个[[开放标准|开放]][[身份验证|认证]]标准<ref name="Google 安全钥匙">{{cite web | url=http://www.smh.com.au/digital-life/consumer-security/google-security-keys-may-offer-extra-layer-of-online-protection-20141105-11dmca.html | title=Google security keys may offer extra layer of online protection | publisher=Fairfax Media | work=The Sydney Morning Herald | date=2014-11-05 | accessdate=2014-11-28 | author=Turner, Adam | archive-date=2015-01-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115032353/http://www.smh.com.au/digital-life/consumer-security/google-security-keys-may-offer-extra-layer-of-online-protection-20141105-11dmca.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，使用专门的[[通用串行總線|USB]]或[[近場通訊|NFC]]设备来加强<ref name="使用安全钥匙">{{cite web | url=https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/6103523?hl=zh-Hans | title=使用安全密钥进行两步验证 | publisher=Google Inc. | accessdate=2015-12-07 | archive-date=2016-06-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603095914/https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/6103523?hl=zh-Hans | dead-url=no }}</ref>并简化<ref name="USB钥匙可以消除麻烦">{{cite web | url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2836692/how-the-fido-alliances-u2f-could-simplify-two-factor-authentication.html#tk.rss_all | title=How a USB key drive could remove the hassles from two-factor authentication | publisher=IDG Consumer & SMB | work=PCWorld | date=2014-10-21 | accessdate=2014-11-28 | author=Bradley, Tony | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112004926/https://www.pcworld.com/article/2836692/how-the-fido-alliances-u2f-could-simplify-two-factor-authentication.html#tk.rss_all | dead-url=no }}</ref>[[双因素认证|双因素认证]]，基于在[[智能卡|智能卡]]<ref name="FIDO 通用第二因素">{{cite web | url=https://www.yubico.com/applications/fido/ | title=FIDO Universal 2nd Factor | publisher=Yubico AB | accessdate=2014-11-28 | archive-date=2016-03-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319141802/https://www.yubico.com/applications/fido/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>中使用的类似安全技术<ref name="Google希望淘汰密码">{{cite web | url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/amadoudiallo/2013/11/30/google-wants-to-make-your-passwords-obsolete/ | title=Google Wants To Make Your Passwords Obsolete | publisher=Forbes.com LLC | work=Forbes | date=2013-11-30 | accessdate=2014-11-28 | author=Diallo, Amadou | archive-date=2015-12-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151217071100/http://www.forbes.com/sites/amadoudiallo/2013/11/30/google-wants-to-make-your-passwords-obsolete/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。它最初由[[Google|Google]]和[[YubiKey|YubiKey]]开发，含有[[NXP|NXP]]的贡献，该标准<ref name="FIDO 联盟标准">{{cite web | url=https://fidoalliance.org/specifications/download/ | title=FIDO Alliance – download specifications | publisher=FIDO Alliance | accessdate=2015-10-13 | archive-date=2018-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180924225117/https://fidoalliance.org/download/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>目前由[[FIDO联盟|FIDO联盟]]运作管理。<ref name="USB钥匙可以消除麻烦" /><ref name="Google账号现在支持安全钥匙了">{{cite web | url=http://krebsonsecurity.com/2014/10/google-accounts-now-support-security-keys/#more-28412 | title=Google Accounts Now Support Security Keys | work=Krebs on Security | date=2014-10-14 | accessdate=2014-11-28 | author=Krebs, Brian | archive-date=2021-01-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121013336/https://krebsonsecurity.com/2014/10/google-accounts-now-support-security-keys/#more-28412 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 支援 ==
=== 服務 ===
U2F安全钥匙可作为一种额外的在线服务两步验证方式，[[Google|Google]]<ref name="Using Security Key">{{cite web|url=https://www.yubico.com/support/knowledge-base/categories/articles/browsers-support-u2f/|title=What browsers support U2F?|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=Yubico|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818004610/https://www.yubico.com/support/knowledge-base/categories/articles/browsers-support-u2f/|archive-date=2017年8月18日|dead-url=yes|accessdate=August 17, 2017|df=}}</ref>、[[Dropbox|Dropbox]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://blogs.dropbox.com/dropbox/2015/08/u2f-security-keys/|title = Introducing U2F support for secure authentication|date = August 12, 2015|accessdate = August 12, 2015|website = Dropbox Blog|last = Heim|first = Patrick|first2 = Jay|last2 = Patel|archive-date = 2018-11-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181115091531/https://blogs.dropbox.com/dropbox/2015/08/u2f-security-keys/|dead-url = yes}}</ref>、[[GitHub|GitHub]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://github.com/blog/2071-github-supports-universal-2nd-factor-authentication |title=GitHub supports Universal 2nd Factor authentication |date=October 1, 2015 |accessdate=October 1, 2015 |website=github.com/blog |publisher=[[GitHub|GitHub]] |last=Olsen |first=Risk |archive-date=2017-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717085632/https://github.com/blog/2071-github-supports-universal-2nd-factor-authentication |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[Gitlab|Gitlab]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://about.gitlab.com/2016/06/22/gitlab-adds-support-for-u2f/|title = Support for Universal 2nd Factor Authentication|date = June 22, 2016|accessdate = July 9, 2016|website = GitLab Blog|last = Nwaigwe|first = Amara|archive-date = 2019-05-31|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190531022825/https://about.gitlab.com/2016/06/22/gitlab-adds-support-for-u2f/|dead-url = no}}</ref>、[[Bitbucket|Bitbucket]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://blog.bitbucket.org/2016/06/22/universal-2nd-factor/|title = Universal 2nd Factor (U2F) now supported in Bitbucket Cloud|date = June 22, 2016|accessdate = June 22, 2016|website = Bitbucket Blog|last = Kells|first = TJ|archive-date = 2018-08-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180808111625/https://blog.bitbucket.org/2016/06/22/universal-2nd-factor/|dead-url = no}}</ref>、[[Nextcloud|Nextcloud]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nextcloud.com/blog/nextcloud-11-sets-new-standard-for-security-and-scalability|title=Nextcloud 11 sets new standard for security and scalability|publisher=Nextcloud|accessdate=23 December 2016|archive-date=2019-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521045935/https://nextcloud.com/blog/nextcloud-11-sets-new-standard-for-security-and-scalability/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[Facebook|Facebook]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/notes/facebook-security/security-key-for-safer-logins-with-a-touch/10154125089265766|title=Security Key for safer logins with a touch|publisher=Facebook|accessdate=27 January 2017|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416135619/https://www.facebook.com/notes/facebook-security/security-key-for-safer-logins-with-a-touch/10154125089265766/|dead-url=no}}</ref>等服务<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dongleauth.info/|title=USB-Dongle Authentication|publisher=Josh Davis|accessdate=22 February 2017|archive-date=2017-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223172410/http://www.dongleauth.info/|dead-url=no}}</ref>已提供支持。

=== 用戶端 ===
[[Google_Chrome|Google Chrome]] 38版和[[Opera浏览器|Opera]] 40版起支援U2F。微软计划在[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://blogs.windows.com/business/2015/02/13/microsoft-announces-fido-support-coming-to-windows-10/|title = Microsoft Announces FIDO Support Coming to Windows 10|date = 2015-02-13|accessdate = 2015-10-03|website = Windows Blog|last = Ingalls|first = Dustin|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151004052701/https://blogs.windows.com/business/2015/02/13/microsoft-announces-fido-support-coming-to-windows-10/|archive-date = 2015-10-04|dead-url = yes}}</ref>和[[Microsoft_Edge|Edge]]浏览器<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://dev.modern.ie/platform/status/fido20webapis/|title = Developer Resources - Platform Status|accessdate = 2015-10-03|website = Microsoft Edge Dev|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151004081624/https://dev.modern.ie/platform/status/fido20webapis/|archivedate = 2015年10月4日|df = }}</ref>中支持FIDO 2.0。[[Mozilla|Mozilla]]正在向[[Firefox|Firefox]]增添支持，目前可以安裝附加元件方式支援，在Firefox 57以上版本則可設定瀏覽器原生支援。<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1065729|title = Bug 1065729 - Implement the FIDO Alliance u2f javascript API|accessdate = November 2, 2015|website = Mozilla Bugtracker|archive-date = 2021-05-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210510073726/https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1065729|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/u2f-support-add-on/ | title=U2F Support Addon | accessdate=May 8, 2016 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224032122/https://addons.mozilla.org/en-Us/firefox/addon/u2f-support-add-on/ | archive-date=2016-12-24 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.yubico.com/2017/09/firefox-nightly-enables-support-fido-u2f-security-keys/|title = Firefox Nightly enables support for FIDO U2F Security Keys|accessdate = September 27, 2017|website = Yubico blog|archive-date = 2017-09-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170927155356/https://www.yubico.com/2017/09/firefox-nightly-enables-support-fido-u2f-security-keys/|dead-url = no}}</ref>
